'''惡魔羊腰'''（Devilled kidneys）是一道[[英國|英國]]料理，在煮熟的羔羊[[腎臟|腎臟]]上淋上以[[伍斯特醬|伍斯特醬]]、[[芥末醬|芥末醬]]、[[牛油|牛油]]、{{tsl|yue|牛角椒}}、[[黑胡椒|黑胡椒]]與[[食鹽|鹽]]調和的「惡魔醬」而成。<ref name=hairybikers>{{cite news|title=Devilled kidneys|url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/devilled_kidneys_58867|accessdate=2012-07-28|newspaper=BBC Food|archive-date=2012-08-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120826054717/http://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/devilled_kidneys_58867|dead-url=no}}</ref>有關該菜餚的紀錄最早見於18世紀，至[[維多利亞時代|維多利亞時代]]開始風行於上流階級，常作為早餐與[[紳士俱樂部|紳士俱樂部]]宴會菜餚；如今則作為晚餐菜食用。<ref name=offallslater>{{cite news|last=Slater|first=Nigel|title=Oooh, you are offal...|url=https://www.theguardian.com/lifeandstyle/2001/nov/04/foodanddrink.recipes|accessdate=2012-07-28|newspaper=The Observer|date=2001-11-04|archive-date=2013-08-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130825211914/http://www.theguardian.com/lifeandstyle/2001/nov/04/foodanddrink.recipes|dead-url=no}}</ref>

